          "vnum": 40406,
          "name": "Guard Commanders Office",
          "description": "The office of the commander of the city guard is surprisingly simple and utilitarian. A plain rug covers the stone floor and is topped by a sturdy wooden desk with a large, high backed chair behind it and two wooden chairs sitting before it. A map of Mareldja plasters one wall, complete with markings to indicate different patrols. A plated door leads to the west, and a large window overlooks the practice field to the east.",
